if you open an NRT reader while addIndexes* is running it may miss segmentsEarwin spotted this in pending ongoing refactoring of Dir/MultiReader, but I wanted to open this separately just to make sure we fix it for 3.1...

This is the fix:
{code}
Index: src/java/org/apache/lucene/index/DirectoryReader.java
===================================================================
